Package: plotlycsv
Type: Package
Title: Export Plotly Trace Data to CSV in Static HTML (Quarto/R Markdown)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Russell", family = "Politzky", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "russell.politzky@firstrand.co.za")
    )
Description: Adds a custom Plotly modebar button to download the data currently
    rendered in a plotly htmlwidget (including ggplotly output) as a CSV file.
    Designed for static HTML outputs such as Quarto and R Markdown (no Shiny server required).
